@startuml sequence_deep_review
title 深度合同审查流程时序图

actor User
participant "DeepReportPage" as UI
participant "FastAPI\n/api/v1/ai/deep-review" as API
participant "AI Review Service" as Svc
participant "LLM (Claude)" as LLM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> UI: 点击"开始深度审查"
UI -> API: POST /deep-review/run
note right
    Input: {
        "document_id": 123,
        "review_depth": "deep",
        "user_role": "承租方"
    }
end note

API -> DB: SELECT documents WHERE id=123
API -> Svc: run_deep_review(doc, user_role)

== Intake Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 识别文书基础信息
LLM --> Svc: {contract_type, jurisdiction, parties, amount, term}

== Clause Mapping Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 切分条款
LLM --> Svc: clause_list[]
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO clauses

== Issue Spotter Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 审查清单 + clauses → 识别风险
LLM --> Svc: risk_items[] + missing_clauses[]

== Legal Research Agent ==
Svc -> DB: SELECT legal_sources (预置法条库)
Svc -> LLM: 法条匹配 + 案例检索
LLM --> Svc: citations[] (含 source_type, authority_level, applicability_reason)

== Citation Validator Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 校验引用是否存在/匹配/过度推断
LLM --> Svc: validation_results[] (pass/fail/correction)

== Senior Lawyer Review Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 复核风险等级/法律分析/替代条款
LLM --> Svc: review_adjustments[]

== Drafting Agent ==
Svc -> LLM: 生成三版本替代条款
LLM --> Svc: {conservative, balanced, bottom_line} per risk

== Report Assembly ==
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO review_reports
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO risk_items[]
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO source_citations[]
Svc --> API: report_id

API --> UI: 返回完整报告
note right
    Output: {
        "report_id": 456,
        "report_meta": {
            "risk_score": 72,
            "risk_level": "高",
            "signing_recommendation": "修改后签署",
            "lawyer_review_required": true
        },
        "executive_summary": {...},
        "contract_summary": {...},
        "risk_matrix": [{risk_id, title, risk_level, probability, severity}],
        "risk_items": [{
            "risk_no": "R-001",
            "title": "押金返还条件不明确",
            "risk_level": "高",
            "legal_analysis": {...},
            "citations": [{source_name, source_type, authority_level, verification_status}],
            "revision_plan": {conservative, balanced, bottom_line}
        }],
        "missing_clauses": [...],
        "favorable_clauses": [...],
        "legal_authority_appendix": [...],
        "disclaimer": "..."
    }
end note

UI -> User: 渲染深度报告

@enduml